body:
Could reproduce this panic.
The validates okay, expands okay, flattens without error but fails when marshaling the YAML using yaml.v3.
Evrything is fine when marshaling to JSON.
The culprit definition are some empty "cause" fields: there is a bug in swag MarshalYAML that doesn't handle null values correctly. Fixing it.

issue.title: fix(yaml): handled null values from JSON

repository.name: swag
repository.description: goodie bag in use in the go-openapi projects

issue.title: fix(yaml): fixed panic when MarshalYAML returns an error
